videos.headline: Clemson RB escapes for 75-yard TD on opening play
videos.description: Clemson strikes on the first play of the game as Travis Etienne avoids Pittsburgh defenders for a 75-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Clemson's Etienne powers in 2nd TD of the game
videos.description: Travis Etienne is dominating early, as he powers in a 3-yard Clemson touchdown his second of the day.

videos.headline: Pitt RB leaps over defenders for 1-yard TD
videos.description: Pittsburgh continues to chip away at Clemson's lead as Qadree Ollison dives over the pinline for a 1-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Lawrence threads the needle for 5-yard TD
videos.description: Clemson answers as Trevor Lawrence throws a dime to Tee Higgins for a 5-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Lawrence throws a dart for 2nd TD
videos.description: Clemson's pulling away as Trevor Lawrence finds Tee Higgins for his second touchdown of the game.

videos.headline: Clemson RB fights for 1-yard TD
videos.description: Clemson's Adam Choice powers through the line for a 1-yard touchdown.
